Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=191}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:16.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bene. A breve arriverà il CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:19.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin! Entra nel treno marino per prima.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non perdere tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:24.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, voi! Forza, portatela su!{direbbe solo portatela}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:24.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sì!\N– Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:32.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Funzionari del governo, marine... \NE la cara Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:37.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bene... Come dovrei comportarmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:42.31,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(16,58,\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\4a&H78&)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(17,433,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}{\t(3978,4437,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}{W7 08 @10:19}Io ho un'oscurità che non conoscete.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A me sembra proprio che \Nla stiano portando via...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:53.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Con avversari di quel calibro, se volesse sfuggirgli, \Ndovrebbe riuscire a sconfiggergli facilmente anche da sola...{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che abbia qualche secondo fine?{penso intenda robin}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oppure che abbia una ragione \Nper cui non può fuggire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.42,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Perdona l'attesa, dolce Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:11.59,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ti stavo aspettando, mio unico principe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:20.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O forse lo sta facendo apposta \Nperché vuole che la salvi {\i1}io{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Signor Corgi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È arrivato il CP9.{sarebbe "è il cp9"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.41,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Bastardo! Lasciami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.41,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Ti ho detto di lasciarmi andare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:44.04,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vi ho detto che ho paura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È il signor Rob Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Impressionante!{di suo è tipo "che potenza", ma intenso come "presenza intensa", non so se mi spiego}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quello... è il CP9?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quante volte devo dirvelo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.55,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mi fate paura!{non si sente granché}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lasciatemi andare, maledetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lasciatemi andare!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dannazione!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:02.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dove volete portarmi?! \NNon vi perdonerò mai, bastardi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ve la farò pagare! Ehi!{circa}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vi avverto, ho ben ottomila sottoposti...{frase non completa in jp}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Congratulazioni per aver concluso \Ndella vostra lunga missione!{cps... ma quella lett è tipo "grazie per il vostro duro lavoro nella lunga missione" che mi suona malissimo, specie perché tizio qua mi pare di grado più basso}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Signor Lucci, il suo cappotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:20.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che esagerazione...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:22.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Falli smettere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sì! S-Subito!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non è un gioco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rimanete concentrati!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Salite tutti sul treno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tutti sul treno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:38.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pronti alla partenza per Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vi ho detto di lasciarmi andare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:45.89,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma che diavolo fanno quei due?{suppongo che con aitsura intenda franky e usopp}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Però...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:52.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Throwback to W7 04 @24:20}{\q2}Ma quale "vi ho causato problemi fino alla fine".{è solo un ref, non un vero flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Intendi causarci problemi anche \Ndopo aver lasciato la ciurma?{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Un po' più a destra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Spruzzate dell'acqua!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fate uscire più acqua!{ew}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:05.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Allora... Robin non ci odia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esatto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che sollievo!{per fortuna}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:13.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\an8\q2}Nota: "Tanuki" significa "cane procione" ed \Nè anche una figura del folklore giapponese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh?! È diventato un tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È diventato un tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi! È diventato un tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:18.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quindi, Chopper, dobbiamo cercare in fretta \NLuffy e gli altri e andare a salvare Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ho capito! Lo cercheremo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma dov'è?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Proprio perché non lo sappiamo, \Ndobbiamo cercarlo.{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Farò del mio meglio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:31.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Woah! È diventato un gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aspettate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Inseguire Nico Robin è una vostra scelta,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:44.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ma stanotte alle undici il treno marino \Nsalperà trasportando funzionari del governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:49.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È una mia ipotesi, \Nma è probabile che ci saliranno.{non intende solo robin}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,In pratica,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:53.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin sarà con loro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:54.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dopodiché il servizio del treno marino \Nverrà sospeso temporaneamente.{"il servizio" l'ho aggiunto io}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:02.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Questo perché a breve arriverà l'Aqua Laguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Allora... questo vuol dire che...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:11.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Se vi lascerete scappare quella corsa, non potrete nemmeno più \Nsalpare con una nave e non riuscirete a lasciare quest'isola.{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non ci credo! Che guaio! \NChe ore sono adesso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Le dieci e mezza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Ma mancano solo trenta minuti!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, non puoi fare qualcosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ferma il treno marino per un po'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:28.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Beh... La meta è Enies Lobby, un'isola su cui solo \Ni membri del governo possono mettere piede.{in realtà è tipo "un'isola vietata a tutti tranne che ai membri del governo"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:32.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Anche il macchinista è parte del governo, \Nperciò non mi darebbe retta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... Allora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non posso far altro che andare in qualche \Nmodo in stazione a convincere Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:40.21,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:44.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ti dirò da che parte sono volati via Luffy e \NZoro, perciò vai a cercarli da quelle parti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se dovessi trovarli, \Ndigli di venire subito in stazione!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sì! Ok, ho capito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, voialtri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Signor Paulie, sta bene!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:59.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Date una mano a quella ragazza.{sarebbe a quella ragazza e "agli altri", ma gli altri è chopper... non so come metterla}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Eh?!\N– Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,D-Dare una mano? Ma signor Paulie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:07.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sono loro ad aver attentato \Nalla vita del signor Iceburg, no?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dovremmo tenerli entrambi sotto custodia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}E il signor Lucci e il signor Kaku sono ancora dispersi...{deve starci in una riga}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.04,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,È vero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,La ciurma di Cappello di Paglia \Nnon è la colpevole dell'assassinio!{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sono innocenti!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:21.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I veri colpevoli li hanno incastrati e \Nhanno fatto in modo che noi li incolpassimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:28.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Non conosco la loro identità, ma i Cappello di \NPaglia hanno combattuto contro i tizi con le maschere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:34.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,In effetti, è solo merito loro se io e il signor \NIceburg siamo ancora in vita.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:40.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Non dovete preoccuparvi di cercare Lucci e Kaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:44.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Potremmo non incontrarli mai più.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:48.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Lei sa cos'è successo \Nal signor Lucci e agli altri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sono tornati al loro paese.{meh}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:52.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma è assurdo! \NPerché in un momento così importante?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lasciate perdere e cercate Cappello di Paglia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, donna spudorata!{stesso termine di W7 03 @09:10}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ancora... con quel modo di chiamarmi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vuoi andare alla stazione, no? Ti farò strada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Grazie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Signor Paulie! Aspetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sta' dicendo il vero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Piantatela di parlare a vanvera \Ne mettetevi all'opera!{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}O volete forse infangare il nome della Galley-La?!{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– S-Sì, caposquadra!\N– S-Sì, caposquadra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:16.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mi dispiace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:17.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Scusate!\N– Scusate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dateci gli ordini! Vi aiuteremo!{daremo una mano, ma già così cps rosellini chiari chiari}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Prendete gli yagara! Aprile le gabbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sì!\N– Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Tornati al loro paese"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:32.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dire di più complicherebbe le cose.{adattata}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:37.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A provare quel genere di sentimenti... \Nbastiamo io e lei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ragazzi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}Usopp, torna da noi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ditelo anche voi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ok, capito! Uomini, pronti?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sì!\N– Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:14.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:15.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}Usopp, torna da noi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Gira sul quel canale!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È una scorciatoia per la stazione!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:43.44,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ancora venti minuti alla partenza!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.94,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Non andare, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.78,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Non puoi sacrificarti da sola!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.03,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Non te lo perdoneremmo mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:54.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yagara! Ti prego! Più veloce!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ultima corsa, ore undici.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:14.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Partenza dalla Blue Station di Water Seven, \Narrivo ad Enies Lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:16.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:17.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che male!{ahi[a]}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,State lì tranquilli!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:23.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Bastardi, trattateci con più rispetto, brutti idioti!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esatto, esatto, idioti!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maledetti bastardi del governo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh, ah, no... Quello non...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A causa dell'avvicinarsi dell'alta marea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:34.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i0}l'orario di partenza sarà anticipato. \NLa partenza è imminente.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maledizione... Sta per partire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:44.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,La nostra missione è quasi completata, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:49.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non fare commenti così alla leggera \Nfinché non saremo arrivati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Brutta idiota.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chiedo scusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:11:00.85,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(23,63,\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\4a&H78&)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(23,357,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}{06:06}Se vi lascerete scappare quella corsa, non potrete nemmeno più \Nsalpare con una nave e non riuscirete a lasciare quest'isola.{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ti prego, fa' che sia in tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.49,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:19.24,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Bastardo... stai bene?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:30.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cappello di Paglia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dove siete?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi! Dove siete?!{<sanji va}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Venite fuori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:44.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fscx80\fscy80\bord3.04\shad3.04}Usopp, torna da noi!{<usopp va lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:51.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Robin è stata portata via!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:53.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rispondimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dove sei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cosa staranno facendo Luffy e gli altri?{circa}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:11.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qualcuno riuscirà ad arrivare qui in tempo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:17.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}Ripeto. La partenza dell'ultima corsa è imminente.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maledizione!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:27.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,399)}Q-Quei bastardi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:31.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,396)}Non li perdonerò mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mi sono incastrato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Aver fatto un passo falso mi ha portato alla rovina.{adattato}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:46.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maledizione.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mi sono incastrato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:02.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Venite fuori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Andiamo a salvare Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Cappello di Paglia!\N– Cappello di Paglia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:10.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ragazzi... ma dove siete?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Da questa parte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:21.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cappello di Paglia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non ci sono proprio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Possibile siano ai sobborghi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Se fosse così, la zona potrebbe già essere allagata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Anche andare a cercarli sarebbe pericoloso!{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maledizione!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:37.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cappello di Paglia! Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Signor Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:50.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Le onde stanno diventando piuttosto alte, \Nperciò, anche se in anticipo, partiremo a breve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qualcosa in contrario–
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.35,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sì! Allora...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ci abbiamo vissuto cinque anni,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:04.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ma non provo un briciolo di \Nnostalgia per questo posto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi! Avete sentito anche voi \Nquel fischio del treno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sì! Ma è strano! Non è ancora ora che parta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Però non ci sono passeggeri normali.{nel senso son tutti del governo}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:37.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È possibile che, vedendo il tempo, \Nabbiano deciso di partire in anticipo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Veloci! Si vede il davanti della stazione!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:43.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fermati, treno marino!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:54.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1}Ultima corsa del treno marino per oggi. \NPartenza a Water Seven, arrivo ad Enies Lobby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Si parte! Sedetevi ai vostri posti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:01.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sta per partire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:09.43,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(17,58,\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\4a&H78&)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(17,434,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)\q2}Mi hai salvato la vita quando desideravo morire.{ALA 21 @ 12:48}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.85,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2483,0,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Quello è il tuo crimine.{ALA @ 12:52}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:21.19,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(16,58,\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\4a&H78&)\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&\t(16,433,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)\q2}{ALA 21 @ 12:54 - EL08 @ 03:48}Non ho né destinazione né posto in cui tornare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.07,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Quindi... lasciami stare su questa nave.{ALA 21 @ 12:57}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:28.53,FlashbacksSecondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mellorine! Mellorine! Mellorine! Mellorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:27.07,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, capisco! \NAllora non c'è scelta! Va bene!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.53,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,– Luffy!\N– Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:31.37,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Non preoccupatevi!{ALA 21 @ 13:05}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:34.04,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2229,0,1,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Non è una persona cattiva!{ALA 21 @ 13:07}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Si sta muovendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Maledizione... Dannati funzionari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Siamo arrivati! Grazie, yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Scendi le scale dall'entrata centrale!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin, non andare!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, tu, chi sei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È pericoloso, allontanati!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin, scendi dal treno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Noi... combatteremo contro chiunque!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:32.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dove siete?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non riesco a uscire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aspetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fermati, treno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aspetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:05.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:15.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non hai fatto in tempo?
Comment: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:39.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C-Che male...{già commento, la coerenza degli inglesi a volte non so}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma che intenzioni aveva quel tizio?{direbbe quell'uomo}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qualunque fossero state
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.01,0:17:47.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,quel treno è riservato del governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:49.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Una volta catturato, sarà la fine per lui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lui è della Galley-La...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:59.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non essere inopportuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sembra sia una faccenda delicata...
Comment: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:03.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Le stazioni sono luoghi di incontri e di addii!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:12.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ed è nostro compito come addetti della \Nstazione vegliare sul tutto in silenzio, no?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hai ragione.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fai silenzio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È partito piuttosto in anticipo, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:24.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Eh?!\N– Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:28.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tutti i passeggeri erano già a bordo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Inoltre
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:33.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,il mare è più agitato di quanto previsto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:38.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh... Di questo passo, l'Aqua Laguna \Npotrebbe arrivare da un momento all'altro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Perciò la partenza è stata anticipata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Questo posto è pericoloso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:45.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sarebbe meglio evacuare nell'isola dei \Ncantieri al più presto...{cps e ho tagliato navali}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:46.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hai ragione.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:52.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, tu. Una volta partito, \Nil treno non può essere fermato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È difficile dirlo, ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,quel luogo detto Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Stai piangendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beh... Ecco... Capisco come ti senti...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lo seguiremo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Era arrabbiata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:12.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non li posso proprio perdonare \Nquegli idioti del governo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:14.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi! Prestami una nave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma che cavolo stai dicendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Una nave grande e forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vuoi salpare su quel mare?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bastarda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:24.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non dire sciocchezze quando non capisci \Nquanto terribile sia l'Aqua Laguna!{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,La supererò!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È ben diversa dall'alta marea che immagini!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:32.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Presto la furia del mare sarà spaventosa!{ew}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non è possibile partire per mare ora! \NSarebbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,come andare verso la propria morte!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:40.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Però... Anche Robin sta \Nsacrificando la sua vita per noi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che rischio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,G-Grazie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:17.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Signor Paulie! Mille grazie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:21.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Il mare stava per trascinarci via...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guarda bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:26.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quel gigantesco tabellone orario \Nè stato strappato via dalle onde.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:31.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Non è... mai successa una cosa simile prima d'ora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma che razza di forza è?!{la traduzione che trovo è "forza di attrazione" -.-}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È in fase di avvicinamento ed è già così?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:46.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,La velocità delle onde di questa \NAqua Laguna... è fuori dal comune!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:47.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:50.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Il treno marino su cui è salita Robin sarà al sicuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:56.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Il treno marino dovrebbe superare la zona tempestosa \Nappena prima che arrivi l'alta marea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:21:00.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Supererà anche tutte le onde più alte \Nse non viene colpito in modo diretto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi. Nami saresti tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nella piazza di fronte alla stazione\N c'era una lettera...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:10.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Viene da un tuo compagno, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Una lettera? Da parte di chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sei stato bravo a trovare una cosa così piccola.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:20.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qui! Era abbandonata qui!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Brutto cretino...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cosa c'è scritto?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh... Aspetta un attimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,La prima parte è solo un'inutile love letter.{vedete voi se volete tradurre}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:39.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Love letter"? Dev'essere il terzo uomo!{immagino tipo un triangolo amoroso per sti due, tra Paulie, Nami e Sanji}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:43.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vista la situazione, il terzo uomo è...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cosa sono quegli sguardi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Questa è la parte importante...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.46,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,"P.S:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:58.96,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,ho avvistato Robin mentre \Nsaliva sul treno marino delle undici.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:01.01,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ho deciso di salire anch'io".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.01,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji è sul treno di prima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:06.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E anche Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E anche "un teppista dal ciuffo enorme"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:12.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dev'essere Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.19,0:22:13.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Già, dev'essere lui.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:15.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Un quarto uomo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E il quinto uomo è quel Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:22.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Povero signor Paulie...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:24.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Forse farebbe meglio ad arrendersi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.91,0:22:26.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma che avete, bastardi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:30.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... e poi, con quella lettera, c'era questo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.67,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,"Dentro al treno marino, ci sarà \Nsicuramente almeno un lumacofono.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.38,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ti contatterò il prima possibile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:44.51,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Vorrei che portassi sempre con te
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:46.55,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,quel lumacofono cucciolo \Nche ho comprato in città.{cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:47.55,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Sì,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:50.56,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,pensa a quel lumacofono cucciolo \Ncome se fossi io, il tuo amato–"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:53.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capisco. Ci contatterà usando questo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:57.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Allora aveva già previsto \Nle azioni di Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:22:59.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Incredibile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:22:59.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:06.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Per ora, con Robin c'è Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:09.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Anche noi andremo sicuramente ad Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che cavolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:24.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non riesco neanche a farmi un tiro qua.{una sigaretta}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:27.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Davvero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:30.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji era andato in stazione?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:30.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:35.39,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,E Usopp è sullo stesso treno!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:36.52,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Che sollievo!{per fortuna}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:39.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quindi, indipendentemente da \Ncome raggiungeremo il treno marino,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:43.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,per prima cosa dobbiamo trovare Luffy e Zoro \No non andremo da nessuna parte.{ew cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:44.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ok, ho capito!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:47.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non sbaglio sulla direzione in \Ncui sono stati spazzati via, {cps}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:48.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,perciò cerchiamoli là per ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:51.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Anche voi per favore!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:52.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uomini!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Conto su di voi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sì!\N– Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:57.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lascia fare a noi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:13.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ok, quindi come faccio ad entrare di nascosto?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:16.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wow, che tempesta che c'è qui fuori!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.90,0:24:23.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,233)}Collier Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:28.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chi sei, bastardo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.79,0:24:36.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fermati.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.83,0:24:39.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dove pensi di andare, bastardo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.54,0:24:42.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non muoverti!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:44.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ho visto quel calcio poco fa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.63,0:24:47.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Questo tizio non è un semplice civile!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.01,0:24:51.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sentire...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.60,0:24:55.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,quelle parole così direttamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.27,0:24:59.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mi imbarazza.{ho riso tantissimo facendo i jp sub a questa frase }
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.56,0:25:01.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non ti sto facendo i complimenti!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.15,0:25:02.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che sfrontato!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.94,0:25:07.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi! Fate rapporto a Lucci! C'è un intruso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.07,0:25:08.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fermo dove sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.41,0:25:16.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non mi pare proprio che sia una cosa che \Nvale la pena di riferire al CP9.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.87,0:25:21.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Non importa quanto violento sia la persona sospetta,\N non c'è nulla da temere. Questo perché...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.42,0:25:24.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,in questa carrozza...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.63,0:25:26.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che fumo fastidioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.34,0:25:29.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,...ci sono io, no?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.42,0:25:30.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Signor Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.76,0:25:42.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sai, sono il re dell'isola nel South Blue \Nin cui il karate è popolare.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.77,0:25:43.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esatto. Io...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.69,0:25:45.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,sono un boxing champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.57,0:25:47.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma allora fai karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.86,0:25:54.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Risparmiati tali battute finché \Nnon avrai visto il mio pugno.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.99,0:25:56.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Woah! Così spietato!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.08,0:25:58.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Jerry...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.37,0:26:00.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Aurora Flicker...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.21,0:26:01.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Jab! Jab, jab, jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.58,0:26:05.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Signor Jerry, il nemico è dietro di lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.80,0:26:07.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sei scappato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.92,0:26:10.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Moccioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.05,0:26:16.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Non dovresti pensare che la mia altezza sia \Nuno svantaggio dentro questa piccola carrozza, sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.35,0:26:19.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È la prima volta che vengo \Nripreso da in mezzo alle gambe.{uhm...}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.68,0:26:23.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se non altro, la mia boxe è \Navvantaggiata negli spazi ristretti!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:25.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È lo yoga style!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.23,0:26:27.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yoga one, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.61,0:26:28.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.82,0:26:30.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Il tuo raggio d'azione si è ridotto!{ew}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.65,0:26:33.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Così può sembrare, ma...{in realtà è tipo "così faccio in modo che sembri"}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.07,0:26:34.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Screw...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.82,0:26:38.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Drop Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma quindi ora ignori le regole della boxe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.54,0:26:43.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che spreco di tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.50,0:26:48.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Brochette!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.22,0:27:04.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A partire dalla settima carrozza, \Ni funzionari del governo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.31,0:27:08.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,sono disposti in ordine di forza.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.44,0:27:12.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nella quinta carrozza ci sono quaranta marine
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.40,0:27:16.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,guidati dal capitano del QG della Marina,\N l'ex cavaliere del regno, T Bone.{il glossary inglese dice che nelle vivre card collection è T-Bone}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.41,0:27:18.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nella quinta carrozza
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.58,0:27:24.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}si trova il lottatore del Cipher Pol 7 Wanze che\N farà anche da capo cameriere in questo viaggio.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.91,0:27:30.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E nella terza carrozza c'è il nuovo membro \Ndel CP9, il signor Nero, in attesa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.93,0:27:49.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}In ogni caso, dato che si tratta di un semplice trasporto, \Nnon c'è alcun rischio di attacchi o simili,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.94,0:27:54.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ma in ogni carrozza c'è \Nsufficiente forza militare, perciò...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.74,0:28:01.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cappello di Paglia!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.24,0:28:02.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.74,0:28:04.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Siamo vostri alleati!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.04,0:28:06.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fatti vedere!{vieni fuori}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.46,0:28:08.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cappello di Paglia, dove sei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.50,0:28:12.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Caposquadra! \NDev'essere dura per lei muoversi, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.50,0:28:13.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che ne dice di riposare un po'?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.76,0:28:15.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Idiota! Non è nulla.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.38,0:28:16.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sbrigati a cercare quei due!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.88,0:28:17.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sì!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.05,0:28:21.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Avete informato il signor Iceburg della situazione?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.68,0:28:23.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Due di noi sono andati a fare rapporto!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.40,0:28:33.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dove sta andando?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.86,0:28:35.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Signor Iceburg...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:38.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.74,0:28:40.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cappello di Paglia!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.24,0:28:42.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se ci sentite, rispondeteci!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.58,0:28:44.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.16,0:28:45.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.83,0:28:47.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dove siete?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.00,0:28:53.00,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Ingredienti... dici?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.00,0:28:54.96,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Esatto! Della carne andrà bene!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.96,0:28:58.63,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2\t(2651,3652,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Carne! Portatene quanta più possibile! Sbrigatevi!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.38,0:29:02.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma perché dobbiamo essere sfruttati così?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.97,0:29:05.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No, non è per quella donna.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.14,0:29:09.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Dovremmo dare del nostro meglio per il signor Paulie che,\N nonostante sia stato scaricato da lei, continua a dedicarcisi!{cps grave... non so ridurvela}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.48,0:29:10.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hai ragione!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.02,0:29:14.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Comunque, quella ragazza deve \Navere proprio una fame da lupi!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.57,0:29:17.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sarà in piena crescita... dev'essere così!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.54,0:29:30.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pioggia!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.37,0:29:32.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che guaio...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.96,0:29:36.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Già il mio naso non funziona \Nbene per il forte vento...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.89,0:29:53.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi... Con così tanti di noi che li chiamano,\N non ricevere risposta...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.81,0:29:54.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Possibile che...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.90,0:29:57.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non dire sciocchezze! \NDobbiamo fare tutto il possibile!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.82,0:30:03.11,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Dove siete, Luffy, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.11,0:30:06.41,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Non è da voi farvi battere da quell'uomo-leopardo, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.33,0:30:12.33,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Finalmente... so perché Robin \Nha deciso di allontanarsi da noi!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.33,0:30:14.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dove sei, Cappello di Paglia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.54,0:30:16.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rispondici!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.88,0:30:22.34,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Aspettaci, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.34,0:30:25.51,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Verremo sicuramente a \Nsalvarti con Luffy e gli altri!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.73,0:30:37.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, che succede?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.86,0:30:40.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Signor Paulie! Guardi!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.07,0:30:48.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Più l'acqua si ritrae
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.08,0:30:51.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,più grande sarà l'onda che si formerà.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.20,0:30:55.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Osservandone quanto cala, è possibile intuire \Nl'entità dell'alta marea che ne seguirà.{un po' allungata per comprensione}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.63,0:30:58.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Volo~!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.59,0:31:03.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Beh, considerando quanto è sceso \Nil livello dell'acqua quest'anno...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.59,0:31:06.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Guarda bene, Chimney.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.68,0:31:10.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Woah, incredibile!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.57,0:31:25.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sembra quasi che... il mare si sia prosciugato.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.91,0:31:32.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Non ho mai visto niente di simile negli ultimi decenni.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.83,0:31:38.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Il livello... può scendere così tanto?{molto circa}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.46,0:31:41.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Una cosa così... è la prima volta che la vedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.92,0:31:46.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma che razza di onda enorme arriverà?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.34,0:31:49.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,La totalità dei sobborghi verrà sommersa.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.43,0:31:52.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nei sobborghi non c'è nessuno, vero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.68,0:31:54.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se ci fosse, morirà all'istante!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.48,0:32:04.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Il suono del mare...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.28,0:32:05.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ha smesso...{mi piace di più "non si sente più", ma dice che ha smesso}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.24,0:32:08.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh eh eh eh eh eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.07,0:32:11.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nonna! Guarda, guarda!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.99,0:32:13.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C'è qualcosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.50,0:32:15.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Davvero?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.83,0:32:18.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tra le due case c'è qualcosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.58,0:32:22.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi! Guarda, guarda, guarda, dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.30,0:32:25.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Signora Kokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.13,0:32:28.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, sei la ragazza pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.72,0:32:31.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sorellona pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.22,0:32:32.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, guarda là!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.81,0:32:34.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C'è qualcosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.18,0:32:36.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Qualcosa"?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.52,0:32:40.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che stai dicendo, Chimney?{non so mettervela meglio, la lett è tanto brutta "ma cosa dici da un po', chimney"}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.77,0:32:41.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aspetta...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.52,0:32:44.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ma cos'è questo mare prosciugato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.29,0:32:56.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.33,0:32:59.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quel Cappello di Paglia...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.96,0:33:02.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,non è forse il tuo "Re dei Pirati"?{"omee no toko" sarebbe "dei tuoi"}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.96,0:33:03.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O no?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.26,0:33:08.51,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Quel cretino!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.59,0:33:12.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Ehi, tu! Dove stai andando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.85,0:33:15.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non puoi scendere nei sobborghi!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.31,0:33:17.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non vuoi vivere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.52,0:33:20.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,L'Aqua Laguna sta per arrivare!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.19,0:33:21.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Torna qui!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.77,0:33:25.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che guaio!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.86,0:33:28.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,La donna pirata ha sceso le scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.24,0:33:29.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, torna indietro!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.90,0:33:32.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non andare più in basso!{non andare in basso}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=192}===============================DIALOGUE============================
